Class AlaCarteItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • MenuItem
      • AlaCarteItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class AlaCarteItem
extends MenuItem
    Stores information about an AlaCarteItem to be used in context of a menu such as its name, price, description and the type of AlaCarteItem it is. Inherits various methods from the abstract class MenuItem.
